    "summary": "Carbon neutrality, climate adaptation and resilient urban & rural development are our main tasks nowadays. \n\nHaving worked as a urban planner for more than 25 year in the Netherlands and China, with a lot of experience in urban planning, project process, knowledge exchange between European and Chinese cities, I set up East West Urban Consultancy. Since 2013, the office has been intensively involved in projects on sustainable urban development between NL/EU and China. By offering advice, trainings, workshops, conferences, study visits wherein decision makers, urban planners & experts are involved, we will increase the sense of sustainable development. The cities can learn from each other and will develope in a balanced and sustainable way.  \n\nCore business: \n\n- Advice to NL, EU and China organizations concerning themes on climate change and resilient development.\n- Participating EU projects (function as key expert) cooperating with China in sustainable development. \n- Organizing trainings, delegations & study visit for Chinese cities on sustainable urban development \n- Promoting and match making cooperation between Chinese and their EU partners.\n- Giving lectures, speeches & interviews related to China & EU sustainable urban development \n\nPlease visit our website:ewuc.eu/reference for more information.",
